}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== "Manufactured for CISCO", "SF-100D-05", and "PCB MADE IN CHINA" is silkscreened on one SF100D-05's board (SN: PSJ1622032C, SD205T V01, '''1147''' date code).
The switch IC (QFP, possibly an RTL chip) is covered with a presumably epoxied heatsink.
